Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.15,0:00:07.03,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,We're so happy you could come have lunch with your father and me, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.03,0:00:08.71,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:11.18,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It was super awesome of you to invite me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:13.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Things have been so busy with the Wonderbolts lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:16.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's great to get a chance to relax some place quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:20.14,MrShy,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I intend to do now that I've retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:22.04,MrShy,,0,0,0,,In fact, I converted the back house
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:24.38,MrShy,,0,0,0,,to showcase my cloud collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:27.38,MrShy,,0,0,0,,I have my clouds, your mom has your flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.38,0:00:29.87,MrShy,,0,0,0,,you've got your animals, and your brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:35.43,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,Zephyr Breeze has his… interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.03,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I'll say. Remember when he was convinced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:40.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,square clouds were gonna be the next big thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:44.41,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,He's matured a lot since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:47.65,MrShy,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's funny you bring Zephyr up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.23,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.10,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Not again…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:55.82,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,It's just for a little while, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.33,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,Till he gets back on his hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:00.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wait. You don't mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:02.62,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Guess who's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:03.65,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,That's right, big sis,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.65,0:01:07.41,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,it's your one and only favorite little brother, à moi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:51.42,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Hi, Flutter Butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.42,0:01:54.52,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,How's the bestest big sister ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:56.43,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Hey. Where's the love?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.43,0:01:59.24,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,How about a little excitement to see your baby brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:02.27,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm just surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:05.67,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,When you left, you said mane therapy was your calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:07.60,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Oh, it is, sis, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:11.71,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,You would not believe how much stress ponies hold in their manes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.71,0:02:13.04,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Everything gets limp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:14.50,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Unmanageable!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:18.75,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,No offense, but brushing alone won't solve the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.06,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What went wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.72,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Nothing went wrong per se…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:29.44,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,It's just the powers that be were so locked into their required styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:31.40,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,And you know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:33.07,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I've got my own style!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:35.55,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,And I think they were a little threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.74,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is… lovely, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:48.82,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Rainbows "the best flyer that ever was" Dash…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:51.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Oh, this ought to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.40,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I… I shouldn't tease ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:57.67,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I know the whole super awesome flyer biz is just to impress me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:01.76,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Still, thanks for showing up for my homecoming, it's… it's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.70,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I kinda thought there'd be more ponies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:09.24,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I mean, what about your party planner friend, Sprinkle Pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:13.43,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,She could turn this into a real house party, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.29,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I mean, this place could use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.72,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Dra-a-a-ab.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:19.11,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,I… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.62,MrShy,,0,0,0,,We have been meaning to redecorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:23.95,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Dad, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.58,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,When I'll get all my stuff back in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:28.36,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,you won't even remember what this boring old place looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.67,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Mom, Dad, can I talk to you for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:40.51,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,What is it, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:44.07,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure letting Zephyr to move back home is a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.66,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know you both wanna help, but don't you remember the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.39,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,Zephyr's just trying to find his place, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:52.44,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:55.79,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It just seems like his place always ends up being your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:59.50,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And he, sort of, makes you do everything for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.89,MrShy,,0,0,0,,Well, we may not be as bold as you, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:06.45,MrShy,,0,0,0,,but don't you worry. We know how to stand up for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:12.00,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,And they were all like: "We love your free spirit, Zeph,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:16.43,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,"and it will be wrong to cage that, go follow your dreams!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:22.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Zeph was just telling me all about the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:25.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,ins and outs of mane therapy school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:28.24,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,It's all so political.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.67,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I just could not take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:34.36,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe if you stuck with it for more than a few weeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:37.13,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Sorry sis, but when something's not the right fit,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.13,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,this pony's gotta fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:43.07,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Anyway, good talk, Rainbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.97,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I am so touched you came to see me, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.91,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I hate to deprive you of my presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.48,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,but this breeze needs his Z's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:53.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You know it's the middle of the day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.72,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I know. Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:58.99,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna assume you made up my room the way I like it, right mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.13,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.74,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,All my stuff is out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:05.38,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Wanna grab that for me, pops? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Same old Zeph.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:17.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know you weren't expecting to see your brother, but
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,you've been kinda quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.65,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.34,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I am just so… so…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:26.99,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,so… peeved right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.31,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Excuse my language.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.38,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:36.07,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's me, Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:37.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:44.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.07,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We just had lunch with Fluttershy's parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.92,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And you'll never guess who showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.38,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Mayor Mare? Cranky Doodle Donkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Cheese Sandwich? Miss Harshwhinny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.86,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Zephyr Breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.49,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That makes more sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.51,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And from the look on your face\NI'm guessing it's for another one of his
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,"extended stays"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:08.73,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,She's a bit peeved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.42,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Zephyr is my brother and I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:13.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But he has never learned to do anything for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:17.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't know why my parents are letting him trot all over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:20.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, if your parents won't stand up for themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:23.35,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,maybe you need to stand up for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:25.82,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You know, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:40.53,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Zephyr Breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:41.86,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.42,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Come to see me work my magic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:46.08,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,and turn this place from drab to fab, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:48.17,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Well, watch and learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:50.37,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Can't you see what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:51.61,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:55.88,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I'm getting rid of this old stuff so I can turn the back house into my art studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:59.03,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I decided I'm gonna be a sculptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:01.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about Mom's flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:04.89,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,She's gonna move them so I can have my meditation patio here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:07.07,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,She loves replanting stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.56,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Don't you, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:13.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And Dad's been collecting his favorite bits of cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.95,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,from the factory since before you were born!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:21.53,MrShy,,0,0,0,,The very best from every production run since my first day on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:26.20,MrShy,,0,0,0,,But why hold on to the past, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:30.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You can't just fly in and change everything Mom and Dad have built here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:34.90,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,But this is the only place big enough for my studio slash meditation garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:37.40,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Unless I do it in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:42.81,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know speaking up for yourself can be hard, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:46.04,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But Zephyr will never stand on his own if he can lean on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.08,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Don't be so dramatic, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:52.61,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad just wanna let me be me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.88,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I can do plenty on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I agree, which is why you should move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.37,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, I totally would,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:06.78,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,but I don't think that's Mom and Dad want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.50,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,It's not, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:14.34,MrShy,,0,0,0,,You know we love you son,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.58,MrShy,,0,0,0,,but your sister has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.38,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:20.43,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.02,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I really just came back here to keep…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.08,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,you guys company, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:27.32,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,whatever's best for the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.35,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I j… I just gotta grab a few essentials.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:34.70,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,And you definitely have somewhere else to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:36.95,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.16,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of ponies who'd love for a little…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:40.95,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,breeze to blow their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:50.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, where is Zeph gonna go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:54.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I hope I did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:57.40,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? One hundred percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.30,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Hey si-i-is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:03.70,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Your new roomie is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe like seventy percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:14.69,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Zephyr, when Mom and Dad told you to find some place else to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't think they meant here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:21.89,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not their house, so by definition it's some place else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.49,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Am I right, Rainbows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:28.33,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Stop ogling me and help settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.04,0:09:35.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot that I promised to help Pinkie Pie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.21,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,sprinkle… something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.19,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You said you had plenty of places to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:46.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Fine, you can stay here…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:47.83,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.56,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,We gonna have so much fun…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,On one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.48,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Totally. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You have to get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.57,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Cracking the whip, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.43,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,You always were kind of bossy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.12,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Zephyr Breeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.75,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Kidding. Get a job. Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:18.26,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Where we going so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:23.01,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how bad morning sun is for your mane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:26.17,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Remember how we talked about you getting a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:29.36,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,It was just yesterday, and it's totally on my to-do list,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:33.89,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,but you can't expect me to find something befitting my awesomeness overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:35.74,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I thought you might say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.69,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,So I did it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:39.51,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,These fabrics all need to be dyed those colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:51.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You get started while Fluttershy and I head to the store for more supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:53.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.43,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Thanks for giving my brother a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.43,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I just hope he's up to the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:10.42,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, darling, dying fabric is the simplest thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You just dip cloth in a bath…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.93,0:11:21.64,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Rarity! You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.39,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:27.05,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Since you talk to the animals all the time, I just figured it runs in the family,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:30.00,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,so why not outsource this stuff, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.74,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Turns out that animal communication thing isn't genetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:37.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Zephyr, I asked you to do this job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:40.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Not to put it off on innocent woodland creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:42.18,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.77,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I guess you have some feelings about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:47.13,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,but you should know it's basically your cat's fault
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:49.49,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,for walking by and giving me idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.16,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,But I'm actually kinda into this look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:56.33,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,So I guess what I'm saying is: "You're welcome!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:12:01.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Zephyr, this is just unacceptable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:06.38,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I guess I know when my efforts aren't appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.31,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Those are tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Because they're your new job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:22.78,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,You said you were taking me to the tea with the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:26.31,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Actually, I said I was going to the tea with the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:28.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You're going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.95,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Sis, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Zephyr, it'll be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:37.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just need a pegasus pony to fly up and wipe each window down from top to bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:41.09,Spike,,0,0,0,,And I'm here to make sure you do it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Wow, Zephyr!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This looks amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.92,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Uh, you know, like you said, it was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:54.86,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Where's Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:55.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:00.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to supervise, not do all the work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,I was supervising!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:05.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,And then Zephyr asked me about different cleaning techniques, and which one was best,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,and if I could… Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,I did all the work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:10.64,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Don't let him fool you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:13.43,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Old Spike is quite the taskmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:19.64,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:22.65,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I had to ask Spike to make sure I was doing it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.87,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You didn't do it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:31.76,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, I guarantee there won't be any fooling around on the next job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.23,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Next job?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.99,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's right, Zeph!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:38.84,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You're coming with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:42.82,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,You don't have to come up with some excuse to hang out with me, Rainbows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.90,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Let's just go for a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.93,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,And see where the day takes us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:51.49,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,We're going to Wonderbolts Headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:55.55,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And I am gonna give you a job so simple, and straightforward,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:58.64,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Not even you can weasel your way out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:01.83,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And the second you try I'm gonna zap you with a storm cloud, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:03.07,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:06.35,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I can already feel the electricity between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.11,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash is crazy, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:19.25,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,She expects me to do stuff right when she asks me to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.38,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,It's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.04,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,So you just quit? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:25.09,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Escaped is more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.47,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Besides, what was I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Keep trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Finish something for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.96,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Maybe that way you'd actually find something you like to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:36.19,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,That all sounds fine for your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:37.22,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,But it's just not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.66,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Then I'm sorry, Zephyr, but I don't think you can live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:48.08,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Fine! I'll just go live in the woods like my foreponies before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.77,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Guess the only breeze this zephyr can count on is his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:11.22,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know it was hard, but you did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:15.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You couldn't let Zephyr pull the same stuff on you that he's always pulled on your folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:17.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I guess so…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:20.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Hello, Constance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:23.52,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:29.10,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,See, Wigford? The Breeze needs nopony!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:31.37,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,We've got food, shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:33.60,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Just need to put the old kettle on…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:42.16,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Come on, sticky-sticky…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:43.98,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,make with the sparks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:51.18,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,What's a pony got to do to find a decent stick around here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:02.14,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I know he needs to learn to do things for himself, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:05.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I can't let him to live like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:10.87,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't think he'd make it through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.40,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:17.79,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I was just some…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:19.95,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,cozying up in my sleeping bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:21.83,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Ready to call it an early night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:25.02,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Such an exhausting day, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:28.37,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It's noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:31.84,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,You know me. Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:36.76,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.46,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Zephyr, you're smart and talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:44.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You could do anything if you've just tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:47.46,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,And what if I give everything I have and still fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:50.39,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I think it's better not to try at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:53.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But then you won't ever do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:55.84,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I don't expect you two to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.28,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I mean, when have you ever failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:01.70,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,You literally helped save Equestria like a dozen times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.58,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And I was worried that I fail every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:08.95,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you have to do things even though you might fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.71,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,But failing is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:13.16,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And quitting doesn't feel much better, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.11,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,So here's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:19.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You can come back with me, but you have to do exactly what I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.68,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:24.99,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I will literally do anything you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:27.86,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,If it means I don't have to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:33.58,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Okay, you know what you have to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:36.59,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Thank for help, then quit when I get frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:39.69,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:41.70,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Total opposite of that. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.46,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You think he can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:48.62,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Everypony has times in their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:51.44,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,When their hearts are filled with doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:54.24,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Frustration builds up inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.72,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,And it makes you want to shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:17:59.89,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But if you just take that first step
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The next one will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:05.87,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And you find you can walk, then run,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:10.83,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Then fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:15.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Into the stratosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.42,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You've got to give it your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:22.56,Somepony,,0,0,0,,So you can pass the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:27.92,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Give it everything that you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:30.28,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And we know you can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:33.32,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You just have to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:39.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Have to give it your very best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:43.63,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,There are times when you want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:49.54,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,When you think that you can't go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:54.60,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But if you fight through with all of your might,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:59.95,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You will find that you can't go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:04.02,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That you could do it all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:06.87,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Everypony has times in their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:09.73,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,When their hearts are filled with doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:12.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But if you just give it your all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You'll start to work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:18.20,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,And I know I can't give up too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:21.02,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Get myself in the zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:24.18,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,And I find I can walk then run,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:29.12,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Then fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:33.76,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I can do it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:39.10,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You can do it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:44.81,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I can do it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:48.29,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I can do it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:51.70,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I did it. I actually finished something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:52.86,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,By myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,And it looks exactly like it supposed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.17,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it, Zephyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:58.63,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.09,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,But I do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:02.43,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Thanks for believing in me, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,That's what big sisters are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.82,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, Zeph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.36,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Now that you've accomplished this, what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:12.29,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Anything I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:14.55,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I mean the sky is the limit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:20.33,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,But you know… I've got some baby steps in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Thanks for dinner Mr. and Mrs. Shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It was great as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.38,0:20:27.96,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,Thank you, dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:29.80,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,for not giving up on Zephyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:32.13,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,After all this years of pining for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:35.87,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,It must be so satisfying to see him on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Have you heard from Zephyr?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.88,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Is he doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:41.74,MrShy,,0,0,0,,I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.74,0:20:43.17,MrShy,,0,0,0,,He's a brand new pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:45.52,MrShy,,0,0,0,,So full of drive and determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.47,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:52.67,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Guess who graduated from mane therapy training?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.34,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:57.94,MrShy,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:02.58,MrsShy,,0,0,0,,You look so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.79,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud of you, Zephyr.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:08.90,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,It was only a matter of time before they recognized my true genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:13.64,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,But actually doing the work probably helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.56,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,And I wouldn't have if it weren't for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.16,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I just give you some encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:21.10,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You did this on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:24.93,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,And honestly, right now I feel like I can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.31,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,Except find a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:30.34,ZephyrBreeze,,0,0,0,,I can still crash here for a few days, right?
